                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "We already discussed such implementation details in the past.\nIt was declared that Zend_Translate should not do view-code.\n\nAs option I created a new proposal for adding a Translation_View_Helper... it is not finished for now as I added it some days ago.\nBut this component will add such feature in future.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-09-19T15:18:53.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-09-19T15:18:53.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16818",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "The detailed resons for this decission can be found in these two issues:\n\nhttp:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/browse\/ZF-1096\nhttp:\/\/framework.zend.com\/issues\/browse\/ZF-1116\n",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-09-19T15:35:10.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-09-19T15:35:10.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/16819",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=oetting",
                        "name": "oetting",
                        "displayName": "Jacob Oettinger",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "Thank you for the clarification. \n\nI guess my current helper methods is the way to do it then.",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=oetting",
                        "name": "oetting",
                        "displayName": "Jacob Oettinger",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2007-09-19T15:41:17.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2007-09-19T15:41:17.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/43505",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thadafinser",
                        "name": "thadafinser",
                        "displayName": "Martin Keckeis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I this really planned for the view?\r\n\r\nIt would be nice for classes to just set the complete translation message.\r\n\r\nExample:\r\nReading an excel file from an user and an error occure in cell \"B2\".\r\nThe errors are collected in an array, if you wand to translate it outside (view), you have to collect all untranslated message plus all parameters!\r\n\r\nEasier is to translate and parse the parameter just in the class.\r\nSo currently you have to use the printf function in the parsing class.\r\n\r\n+VOTE for it+",
                    "updateAuthor": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thadafinser",
                        "name": "thadafinser",
                        "displayName": "Martin Keckeis",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "created": "2010-12-07T01:02:18.000+0000",
                    "updated": "2010-12-07T01:02:18.000+0000"
                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/43522",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=thomas",
                        "name": "thomas",
                        "displayName": "Thomas Weidner",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "This issue has been closed more than 3 years ago as won't fix.\r\nWhy do you come to the idea that it is now planned to integrate view code within Zend_Translate?",
